data.description: Discover the charm of this one-story gem with excellent curb appeal that greets you from the moment you pull up to the home. Enjoy the serene atmosphere on the back covered patio, perfect for relaxation. The home boasts some recent updates over the years to both the kitchen and bathroom. The kitchen has cabinets galore, corian and views of the backyard and breakfast area. Beyond, a large backyard workshop space awaits, offering endless possibilities for hobbies or projects. This home also has double pane windows and exterior siding both with a lifetime warranty from Window World.  Solar panels will further help you have an energy efficient home as well!  Embrace comfort and functionality in this inviting home with an easy commute to Lackland AFB, HEB and Walmart.
